text:
With COVID-19 on our minds, Seattle firefighters have created a tiktok video for a #flattenthecurvechallege. Check it out and show us your dance moves! 

Shout out to Marika Theofelis for choreographing this video.

#COVID19 #SocialDistancing https://t.co/Z1EuvK9U3U
